      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "That pain is profound, and your pain is valid, but this very moment of hurt speaks loudly to how much humanity and experience there is still behind you. I am not here to offer false comfort, but to gently suggest that your body and mind are separate from the results you achieved, even if they felt inseparable. If you are in immediate danger, please contact local suicide hotlines or emergency services.",
